# GDScript Patterns

- Use `@export` for inspector-tweakable values
- Prefer composition (components, behaviors) over deep inheritance
- Config classes in `scripts/config/` for balance and tuning
- Signal naming: `snake_case` (e.g. `item_picked_up`, `state_changed`)
- Clear variable names, simple logic, readable structure
- Comments explaining systems. Avoid overly clever code and deep nesting
